entities.description: The numeric code for states as per the Federal Information Processing Standards (FIPS).
The number of respondents from each state, not adjusted for weighting.
The percentage of respondents from each state relative to the total number surveyed.

relationships.description: Indicates the unweighted frequency of respondents from the state identified by the FIPS code.
Indicates the percentage of total respondents from the state identified by the FIPS code.
